Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十一話\N最強的兩人光明與黑暗之戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.66,0:02:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊，你不用怨恨\N最強的維新志士將在此受死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.63,0:02:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你不是為觀柳而戰\N那到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.21,0:02:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時如果\N官兵和幕府在江戶決戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是我們勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在江城堜韙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁著混亂,我們御庭番\N把官兵中樞的志士全部殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.86,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣官兵就群龍無首\N幕府軍就能一口氣打敗官兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一切就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳！我們不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？\N那我現在就在東京做給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.75,0:02:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在說這些已經沒有意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們來說有意義的是\N幕末維新最強的一群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這對我們御庭番高手來說\N才是最好的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.63,0:03:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時侯許多人投入戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.00,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立場雖不同但考慮國家未來\N以及幸福都奉獻自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.64,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你卻不同\N你心中想的只有冷酷的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在還給人民帶來痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我只是區區流浪人\N也不會讓你為所欲為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，蒼紫這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.13,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑他一個嘍囉\N竟敢叫我人渣！絕不可原諒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了！我可以用那個對付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好強！連劍心都被他的劍傷到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要攻破我的防禦是不可能的\N站起來！拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使佔了優勢連笑也不笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！腳怎麼抖個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.15,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.59,0:04:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題！我已經看出\N怎麼防他的小太刀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不像是你會說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓我看看你的能耐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.28,0:05:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比小太刀長的劍\N速度上是無法勝過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.62,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我與你的太刀同時揮劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是為何你的速度變快了\N果然見識到了斬人劍的真髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.10,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也讓你見識\N御庭番真髓作為回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變慢了！為什麼變這麼慢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是四乃森蒼紫\N真正的戰術實戰「劍舞」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.16,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論你拔刀齊有多大能耐\N也抓不到緩急自如的流水動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回天劍舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.05,0:06:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這招到現在為止攻無不克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.56,0:06:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊已死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒！決不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定刺偏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.35,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好氣魄！不過別急著尋死！\N省省力氣吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.05,0:06:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.39,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥。你可是\N神谷活心流的重要繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你在這堻Q殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.93,0:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說我也不想死在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼還有反應！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你砍到的是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來劍心這小子用劍鞘擋住\N讓小太刀的威力減半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.92,0:07:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,號稱維新最強的男子\N我也誠心認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.26,0:07:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過此後最強的稱號\N要拱手讓給我們御庭番了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又使出回天劍舞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我不會刺偏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.21,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說你現在滿身是傷\N動作也變遲鈍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認命吧！緋村拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.92,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用回天劍舞攻擊的瞬間\N會產生漏洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.49,0:08:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿下他的劍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.13,0:08:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫，真想要最強稱號的話\N要多少就有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是對現在的我來說\N那些等著我救助的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.57,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及分享憂喜的朋友們\N比起聲名重要好幾萬倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我。。。竟然輸了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再逞強了！退開！蒼紫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.22,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒結束呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.83,0:08:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事！嗚。。\N可能受點傷不過沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是蒼紫。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.04,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，只是昏迷過去而已\N因強烈痛楚與呼吸困難昏迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.92,0:09:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的好鬥心招致自己的失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.29,0:09:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被回天劍舞打倒時\N你的氣魄讓我很感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦！只是想到要救惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就一股腦地冒出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為。。。為什麼不殺我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我只是個流浪者\N不再用劍斬人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.81,0:10:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼成不了最強的？\N現在最強的已經沒意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.05,0:10:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你能力這麼強\N應該可以用在其他地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他都是為了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.49,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些人在朋友中找到新生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.66,0:10:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能戰鬥的我們生不逢時\N根本沒人會接納我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.73,0:10:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教頭不但沒棄我們於不顧\N甚至拒絕了當士官的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了要安置我們四人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.21,0:10:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以御庭番培養你們的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.62,0:10:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有責任為你們\N爭取最強的光榮名聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.62,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊！你動手殺了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.06,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.56,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂！一切都無所謂了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.90,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快下手，拔刀齊！\N否則日後我還是會殺你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係！隨時歡迎你來挑戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.42,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決不容許你\N把其他人也捲入戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.80,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生不逢時的御庭番與劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.07,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一起把你們解決掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼玩意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.24,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個叫做機關鎗\N可是最新型武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.28,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在揮刀耍劍已經落伍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.39,0:11:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我就證明給你們看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.96,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聲音是。。。\N該不會是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣！厲害吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.47,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一分鐘可發射兩百發子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這混蛋！\N竟打算連同伴都殺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳！你拿那東西做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我觀柳大人！\N你這無禮的傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.67,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來就不想\N只當個秘密賣鴉片的商人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用新型鴉片賺的錢當資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:13:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買進最新型的機關鎗轉賣\N才能賺大錢啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是沒良心的商人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.89,0:13:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算把別人的生活和性命\N當成食物買賣賺錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.93,0:13:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說拔刀齊，有錢的話\N用劍術買不到的都能輕易到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.54,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像這個機關鎗\N錢才是力量的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正最強的是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.09,0:13:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛受夠你的侮辱\N現在就從你開刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.61,0:14:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首。。首領\N你不應該這麼垂頭喪氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.41,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為御庭番一員受你栽培
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在能當首領的擋箭牌\N我就很滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來有誰要受死啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要受死的是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.91,0:14:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.22,0:14:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對。。。對不起！\N首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.26,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到最後。。。還是幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就中鏢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.31,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高荷惠被關在三樓展望室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.42,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊！撿起你的逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿著你\N飛天御劍流獨門寶刀過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.03,0:15:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.83,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！\N熏姑娘和禰彥就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.87,0:15:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領！永別了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.52,0:15:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再往前走了！\N拔刀齊你也將就此結束性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.86,0:16:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一個不是\N無法傷我毫髮就白白送命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧！拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒。饒。。饒命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.01,0:16:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要活命去求你最愛的錢看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打得好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.12,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒。饒。。饒命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧！惠姑娘在等我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！太帥了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們並沒有白白送命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.55,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番四人用他們的性命\N戰勝了觀柳的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.03,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！能遇到你們\N真的很高興。謝謝你們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼？笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.33,0:18:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做鴉片害別人受苦\N只有一死才能贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還說那什麼話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.77,0:18:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心、小姐和禰彥都來救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道要他們白費工夫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.54,0:19:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這女人真不領情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.28,0:19:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使你死了\N那些人也無法死而復生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如活著幫助更多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是想能用劍幫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.70,0:19:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經是人稱斬人拔刀齊的我\N才一直活到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘，我們住得很近\N有空就常來玩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！熏姑娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油喔！惠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！向玄齊醫生學了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後一定努力成為優秀的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀！總有一天\N能與你家人見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那各位，告辭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！我送你到那堙I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.82,0:20:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你倒是在警察面前\N為惠姑娘袒護不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為劍心深受警長信賴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象觀柳那種壞人\N說什麼都沒人會相信他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是問題是在那四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察趕到的時侯\N他和四人的屍體都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定那傢伙\N還打算找劍心挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛。。。誰也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.47,0:21:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今。。。什麼都結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是總有一天。。。

